Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Bungle claim over Iran hostage crisis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h3xs
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Dec 1979
Carter now accused of 'bungling' decision to allow Shah into US for medical treatment, prompting hostage seizure. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less